'''Endor Day''' was a memorial day observed by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] which was held on the anniversary of the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]] in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]] and commemorate the victory of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] over the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

==Behind the scenes==
''[[Star Wars Battlefront: Renegade Squadron]]'' includes special awards for topping score tables on real-life holidays as an [[easter egg]], casting [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Life Day/Legends|Life Day]] as [[Wikipedia:Christmas|Christmas]] and Endor Day as [[Wikipedia:Independence Day (United States)|the Fourth of July]].

